sentences.sentence: Objective: To discuss the diagnostic value of transcutaneous bilirubinometry on neonatal jaundice.
sentences.translation: 目的：探讨经皮测胆红素对新生儿黄疸的诊断价值。

sentences.sentence: This paper introduces the principle and structure of a TENS (Transcutaneous Electric Nerve Stimulation) apparatus.
sentences.translation: 介绍一种恒流型TENS治疗仪的工作原理和结构。

sentences.sentence: Objective: To evaluate the clinical values of transcutaneous bilirubin measurements in diagnosis of neonatal hyperbilirubinemia.
sentences.translation: 目的：评价经皮胆红素测定对诊断、新生儿高胆红素血症中的临床价值。
